And I got to be driftin' alongI don't know if she listened to Bob Dylan, but my Grandma Johnnie Burden did love her southern gospel music. The Gaither Vocal Band was her shit. When I visited her last, she showed me her television that had a DVD player "just for my Gaithers." 

She loved her music. She passed away 24 April, 2025. I thought of her while watching this.
